<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>bool<sp/>m_isInitialized<sp/>=<sp/>false;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">public:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>SparseLU()<sp/>{}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>explicit<sp/>SparseLU(const<sp/>MatrixType&amp;<sp/>matrix)<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>compute(matrix);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>SparseLU&amp;<sp/>compute(const<sp/>MatrixType&amp;<sp/>matrix)<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>//<sp/>LibTorch<sp/>does<sp/>not<sp/>have<sp/>a<sp/>native<sp/>sparse<sp/>LU.<sp/>We<sp/>must<sp/>invoke<sp/>the<sp/>dense<sp/>fallback<sp/>wrapper</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>//<sp/>Coerce<sp/>SparseMatrix<sp/>-&gt;<sp/>Dense<sp/>-&gt;<sp/>linalg_lu_factor_ex</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>at::Tensor<sp/>dense_mat<sp/>=<sp/>matrix.tensor().to_dense();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>std::tie(m_lu,<sp/>m_pivots,<sp/>m_info)<sp/>=<sp/>torch::linalg_lu_factor_ex(dense_mat);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>m_isInitialized<sp/>=<sp/>true;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>return<sp/>*this;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>template<sp/>&lt;typename<sp/>Rhs&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>Rhs<sp/>solve(const<sp/>Rhs&amp;<sp/>b)<sp/>const<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>if<sp/>(!m_isInitialized)<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>throw<sp/>std::runtime_error(&quot;SparseLU<sp/>is<sp/>not<sp/>initialized.&quot;);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>at::Tensor<sp/>dense_b;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>if<sp/>(b.tensor().is_sparse())<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>dense_b<sp/>=<sp/>b.tensor().to_dense();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>}<sp/>else<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>dense_b<sp/>=<sp/>b.tensor();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>at::Tensor<sp/>result<sp/>=<sp/>torch::linalg_lu_solve(m_lu,<sp/>m_pivots,<sp/>dense_b);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>return<sp/>Rhs(result);<sp/>//<sp/>Result<sp/>is<sp/>always<sp/>returned<sp/>dense</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
