<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>SparseLU&amp;<sp/>compute(const<sp/>at::Tensor&amp;<sp/>matrix)<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>at::Tensor<sp/>dense_mat<sp/>=<sp/>matrix.is_sparse()<sp/>?<sp/>matrix.to_dense()<sp/>:<sp/>matrix;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>std::tie(m_lu,<sp/>m_pivots,<sp/>m_info)<sp/>=<sp/>torch::linalg_lu_factor_ex(dense_mat);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>m_isInitialized<sp/>=<sp/>true;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>return<sp/>*this;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>//<sp/>Some<sp/>basic<sp/>compatibility<sp/>hooks<sp/>mapping<sp/>back<sp/>to<sp/>Dense<sp/>equivalents</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>const<sp/>at::Tensor&amp;<sp/>matrixL()<sp/>const<sp/>{<sp/>return<sp/>m_lu;<sp/>}<sp/>//<sp/>Torch<sp/>packs<sp/>L/U<sp/>into<sp/>same<sp/>tensor</highlight></codeline>
